    <section name="Release Notes">
      <subsection name="1.2.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 17 January 2017</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1423">HIPPLUG-1423</a><br/>
            DocumentCopyingPageCopyEventListener improvements:
            <ul>
              <li>
                Better determination and creation of target folder in case the target node structure is different from that of the source.
              </li>
              <li>
                Don't create a new document in the target channel if there already is a linked translated document.
              </li>
              <li>
                Introduction of extension hooks <code>onBeforePageCopyEvent</code> and
                <code>onAfterPageCopyEvent</code> on behalf of customization.
                See at the <a href="custom-configuration.html#Extension_Hooks">custom configuration page</a>.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.1.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 28 December 2015</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Initial release.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
